The Maven team is pleased to announce the 1.0 of Continuum.  

Continuum 1.0 features includes:

 * Support for Maven 2.x
 
 * Support for Maven 1.x
 
 * Support for Ant
  
 * Support for shell scripts

 * Tight integration with Maven SCM

    * Subversion
    
    * CVS
    
    * Starteam

 * Easy to use web-based setup and  interface
 
 * An XML-RPC and SOAP interface for integration, automation and remoting
 
 * Easy to use command line shell interface using Python and the XML-RPC interface
 
 * Mail Notification
 
 * Blame Mechanism 

 * IM notification

   * IRC
   
   * Jabber
   
   * Yahoo!
                
   * MSN
   
For a complete list of changes please refer to:

http://maven.apache.org/continuum/change-log.html
